,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T00:29:52.000Z","msg":"純牛奶香港你買到？<br />\n你不如睇下牛奶係點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港冇整原奶近15年<br />\n即溶咖啡起碼只係溶係水，再固體化<br />\n奶係玩到分開蛋白質+水+近三百度高溫消毒<br />\n水喉水用幾多化學野去整乾淨<br />\n生果用大量農藥/催化<br />\n<br />\n奶/水/糖/即溶咖啡/生果，即溶咖啡已經係最少化學野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:11:16.000Z","msg":"咖啡品質嘅標準就係來自土壤、種植技術、發酵處理等等...每一個種植同處理過程帶來嘅風味<br />\n<br />\n即溶咖啡半點都保留唔到，你叫咖啡撚入來搵高質俾你，梗係搵唔到答案啦。"},{"pid":"6ecea358a665d23756a92fd039e6b74d4d93592d","tid":2180012,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c258dab90ff3c2074f1635aa15aa04c7adf7f04f","tid":2180012,"uid":43473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T18:38:59.000Z","msg":"越南G5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:11:47.000Z","msg":"又平又好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d0e5e3057fe8d5f1463be76a6f77de6da4c365","tid":2180012,"uid":36833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ecea358a665d23756a92fd039e6b74d4d93592d","tid":2180012,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c258dab90ff3c2074f1635aa15aa04c7adf7f04f","tid":2180012,"uid":43473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T18:38:59.000Z","msg":"越南G5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:11:47.000Z","msg":"又平又好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:16:59.000Z","msg":"G7 同 the king coffee都好肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da2341a81424803427943ea6c09863dc84290ae","tid":2180012,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:43:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8cIqLvJz8VM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8cIqLvJz8VM&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=9ffb007f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8cIqLvJz8VM</a>"},{"pid":"15b0a460b56d4edafb01daa1ae784757ef3ea5fb","tid":2180012,"uid